*DESCRIPTION_START
Various paintings of wildlife scenes adorn the wall, painted by various
people, most were Priests in Shemri's service. Several acolytes staff
desks here, working on various tasks. A maple door leads to the office
of the Matriarch. An opening leads into another hallway, towards the
library.
*DESCRIPTION_END
