Number 586
Name Courtyard of Shemri
PLAIN
DAY_LIGHT
REGION 205
*DESCRIPTION_START
This large outdoor area is designed to allow all members of the
Church to experience the nature that the Godess has bestowed. It
is not unusual for studying to be done out here, on the stone
benches, or beneath a shade tree in the lush grass. A pair of
signs frame a serving window, staffed by various priests and
priestesses.
*DESCRIPTION_END
