Number 587
Name Shemri, Sanctuary
REGION 205
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
This area is a lush grove, oak trees, soft grass and svelt moss make
the area quite pleasant to be in. A gently running stream runs across
the area, starting under a small waterfall. A conspicuous empty spot
is left for the altar which has yet to be crafted.
*DESCRIPTION_END
